# Direct CI inputs. Regenerate the hashed lock after dependency changes:
#   uv pip compile --universal --python-version 3.11 --generate-hashes \
#     --no-annotate -o requirements/ci.txt requirements/ci.in
#
# The lock must resolve for the LOWEST version in the CI matrix and carry markers
# for the rest. A lock compiled on 3.12 silently omits dependencies that only
# apply below it (jaraco-context pulls backports.tarfile on < 3.12), and
# --require-hashes then fails on 3.11 with "must have their versions pinned".
